[{"id": "94d9db9f-5612-4352-88d3-fa39d4706f48", "chunk_index": 0, "text": "USER: Hi. i just installed this writing studio? what's next?\nASSISTANT: Hey \u2014 welcome in.\n\nYou're looking at Lagoon. You've got a fresh install with three demo characters: me (your guide), Hermione for actual fiction writing, and Nathan for casual chat.\n\nQuick orientation:\n- **Characters** are your conversation partners \u2014 each has their own system prompt, context, and personality\n- **Anchors** let you bury lore that only surfaces when specific keywords come up (great for secrets, worldbuilding, reveals)\n- The **Style Overseer** panel lets you set quality rules that run after every response\n- Everything's local \u2014 your chats, your configs, your RAG memory index\n\nIf you want to see how a writing-focused character works, open Hermione and start a scene. If you want to poke around the settings first, click the gear.\n\nWhat kind of writing are you looking to do? Or do you want to just explore first?", "embedding": [-0.0059297773987054825, -0.12346431612968445, 0.06963573396205902, 0.015531044453382492, -0.03546421229839325, -0.0003986130759585649, 0.02838214300572872, 0.01448901928961277, 0.01138121634721756, 0.009493920020759106, -0.021945949643850327, -0.019014721736311913, -0.05658775940537453, 0.028887290507555008, 0.03456420451402664, 0.02983323112130165, 0.09126406908035278, -0.08628669381141663, 0.0006702050450257957, 0.016269486397504807, 0.03259038180112839, -0.005057916976511478, 0.04791731387376785, -0.03645703196525574, -0.008470873348414898, -0.015526631847023964, -0.028630012646317482, 0.02065454050898552, -0.029665086418390274, -0.0340765006840229, -0.05553492531180382, 0.05530520901083946, 0.08712723851203918, -0.008096741512417793, 0.06729649007320404, 0.09686915576457977, 0.04855263605713844, 0.011654783971607685, -0.031025085598230362, -0.07448796927928925, -0.0977911651134491, -0.06569822132587433, -0.017826857045292854, 0.07855224609375, 0.07878966629